001
002package com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.product;
003
004import java.util.function.Function;
005
006import com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.*;
007import com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.MoneyQueryBuilderDsl;
008import com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.ReferenceQueryBuilderDsl;
009import com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.product_type.AttributeLocalizedEnumValueQueryBuilderDsl;
010import com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.product_type.AttributePlainEnumValueQueryBuilderDsl;
011
012public interface AttributeQueryBuilderMixin {
013    default CombinationQueryPredicate<AttributeQueryBuilderDsl> plainEnum(
014            Function<AttributePlainEnumValueQueryBuilderDsl, CombinationQueryPredicate<AttributePlainEnumValueQueryBuilderDsl>> fn) {
015        return new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(ContainerQueryPredicate.of()
016                .parent(new ConstantQueryPredicate("value"))
017                .inner(fn.apply(AttributePlainEnumValueQueryBuilderDsl.of())),
018            AttributeQueryBuilderDsl::of);
019    }
020
021    default CombinationQueryPredicate<AttributeQueryBuilderDsl> localizedEnum(
022            Function<AttributeLocalizedEnumValueQueryBuilderDsl, CombinationQueryPredicate<AttributeLocalizedEnumValueQueryBuilderDsl>> fn) {
023        return new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(ContainerQueryPredicate.of()
024                .parent(new ConstantQueryPredicate("value"))
025                .inner(fn.apply(AttributeLocalizedEnumValueQueryBuilderDsl.of())),
026            AttributeQueryBuilderDsl::of);
027    }
028
029    default CombinationQueryPredicate<AttributeQueryBuilderDsl> money(
030            Function<MoneyQueryBuilderDsl, CombinationQueryPredicate<MoneyQueryBuilderDsl>> fn) {
031        return new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(ContainerQueryPredicate.of()
032                .parent(new ConstantQueryPredicate("value"))
033                .inner(fn.apply(MoneyQueryBuilderDsl.of())),
034            AttributeQueryBuilderDsl::of);
035    }
036
037    default CombinationQueryPredicate<AttributeQueryBuilderDsl> reference(
038            Function<ReferenceQueryBuilderDsl, CombinationQueryPredicate<ReferenceQueryBuilderDsl>> fn) {
039        return new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(ContainerQueryPredicate.of()
040                .parent(new ConstantQueryPredicate("value"))
041                .inner(fn.apply(ReferenceQueryBuilderDsl.of())),
042            AttributeQueryBuilderDsl::of);
043    }
044
045    default LongComparisonPredicateBuilder<AttributeQueryBuilderDsl> longNumber() {
046        return new LongComparisonPredicateBuilder<>(BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("value")),
047            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, AttributeQueryBuilderDsl::of));
048    }
049
050    default DoubleComparisonPredicateBuilder<AttributeQueryBuilderDsl> doubleNumber() {
051        return new DoubleComparisonPredicateBuilder<>(
052            BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("value")),
053            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, AttributeQueryBuilderDsl::of));
054    }
055
056    default StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<AttributeQueryBuilderDsl> string() {
057        return new StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<>(
058            BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("value")),
059            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, AttributeQueryBuilderDsl::of));
060    }
061
062}
